do you think you're doing right by your mother?

364
00:36:55,010 --> 00:36:56,880
Give me the Spatial Ring.

365
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:04,199
What is this?

366
00:37:04,200 --> 00:37:06,999
This is my present for you.

367
00:37:07,000 --> 00:37:11,499
No matter what happens in the future,
you must keep this Spatial Ring safely.

368
00:37:11,500 --> 00:37:13,700
My mother instructed me before she left

369
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:18,400
that I must protect this ring well.

370
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:22,900
I will always wear it.

371
00:37:24,700 --> 00:37:27,100
You can drink as much wine as you want.

372
00:37:27,160 --> 00:37:29,199
Anyway, I'm good at enduring a paddling.

373
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:31,200
Just treat it as doing my filial duty toward you.

374
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:36,899
I don't owe anyone, you little brat! How dare you say
that my temper is bad?! I'll kill you with one slap!

375
00:37:36,900 --> 00:37:38,900
You owe me a lot!

376
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:51,599
Father, did you call for me?

377
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:53,199
It's been years since we've seen Yanran.

378
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:54,899
Yanran's here?

379
00:37:54,900 --> 00:37:57,699
The Nalan Clan are currently recruiting talents

380
00:37:57,700 --> 00:38:02,099
to go to Wu Tan City
and attend the Jia Nan Academy examination.

381
00:38:02,100 --> 00:38:03,499
I'll give you leave.

382
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:07,899
Buy some gifts and go visit Yanran.

383
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:12,100
Don't bother. In my current state...

384
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:16,999
The engagement was set
by your grandfather and the Nalan family.

385
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:20,699
Now that both you and Yanran are grown,

386
00:38:20,700 --> 00:38:22,399
it's time for you to see each other.

387
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,999
This is...

388
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:28,800
the visit letter I wrote
for the Clan Chief of the Nalan Clan. Take it with you.

389
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:34,600
- Miss.
- Miss.

390
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:39,799
Good day, Miss.

391
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:43,300
The matter concerning the Xiao Clan
is quite hard to handle.

392
00:38:44,330 --> 00:38:47,760
Xiao Zhan is a stubborn man.

393
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:56,700
I still have things to do,
so I'll take my leave now.

394
00:39:07,600 --> 00:39:09,400
Grandfather.

395
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,500
Who made you angry?

396
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:17,599
This is a letter from your master.

397
00:39:17,600 --> 00:39:19,999
He sent four disciples

398
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:24,499
on an eight hundred li journey
to bring this over quickly.

399
00:39:24,500 --> 00:39:26,900
It's about your marriage.

400
00:39:30,200 --> 00:39:32,399
What Sect Leader Yun Shan said is right.

401
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:36,800
One seeks his way up, just as water seeks its way down.
[T/N: One should always strive to make progress.]

402
00:39:44,200 --> 00:39:46,199
Faster or we'll be late.

403
00:39:46,200 --> 00:39:48,399
