- Wait for me.

404
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:49,999
Young Master.

405
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:51,799
Let me do this kind of work instead, Young Master.

406
00:39:51,800 --> 00:39:54,299
What is it? I'm delivering water
to the martial arts skills training studio.

407
00:39:54,300 --> 00:39:56,219
